<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Put all ingredients in pan, bring to boil then lower heat and cook covered 20-30 mins. Time depends on toughness of carrots. Add water as needed.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[when almost done, increase heat, uncover and toss unil all liquid has evaporated.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Remove from fire and add butter, chopped coriander, lemon juice, and nutmeg]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
